{"tid":1799262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真普選=搞港獨。不服來辯","createTime":"2019-12-26T21:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T23:04:04.000Z","uid":254923,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a825bd27ddbb4c118386ba4fec0a9bf2ad054bda","tid":1799262,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:52:05.000Z","msg":"而家咁樣對於中國共產黨嚟講根本就冇分別<br />\n佢哋視真普選為港獨<br />\n即係真普選=港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢樣野唔係我哋講，而係中共佢哋咁樣認為<br />\n<br />\n你哋究竟有冇腦<br />\n重點唔係我哋要點樣去界定港獨同真普選<br />\n而係中共已經視佢哋兩個係一樣嘅嘢<br />\n你解釋得再清楚都冇撚用啦<br />\n醒未啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有呢一個係法西斯政權<br />\n殺人佢哋絕對唔會手軟<br />\n你仲諗住做有民主嘅中國人？<br />\n一係就做好準備同呢個政權完全切割<br />\n一係就甘心情願做中國人<br />\n<br />\n咁都上唔到熱門嘅話<br />\n證明大部份人仲未知道乜嘢係光復香港，時代革命<br />\n我就係要將說話講到咁撚重㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a08321ef571b2d3bba40d67d77fbab01f29bcbb","tid":1799262,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:53:52.000Z","msg":"我再講多一次港獨同真普選<br />\n某程度根本就係中共去定義<br />\n唔係我哋去解釋就可以<br />\n咁撚樣講仲清唔清楚？"},{"pid":"530f5119c3ccf8e5a5646cf20b8f57a4a04f7a5b","tid":1799262,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T21:55:15.000Z","msg":"：樓主可能係熱狗<br />\n：已經證實樓主係鬼，大家小心<br />\n：$0.5"},{"pid":"36bea1c8ff59e0db1d428d7ab274cefbe68a2d77","tid":1799262,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471b42adaae89998d86356b51fb95b6813906629","tid":1799262,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T22:11:46.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"b6692c6d6e4fb8d84a6b5dd87fb89f78fd26f5ea","tid":1799262,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"471b42adaae89998d86356b51fb95b6813906629","tid":1799262,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,